Exploration enrichment pathways with differentially expressed (DE) genes between old versus young

Team Le Grand

03 mai,2022

Pathway explored : REACTOME BINDING AND UPTAKE OF LIGANDS BY SCAVENGER RECEPTORS

This pathway contain 109 genes.

In these 109 genes for each day and cell type, they are not all expressed and they are not all differentially expressed between old versus young.

Inside these differents genes, there are (cf table below) number of genes DE significant with a major participation in the enrichment (leadingEdge cal by fgsea filter by padj<0.05).
